{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7b4183d9-e1c8-4080-a73f-164b5fd15b1b", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7b4183d9-e1c8-4080-a73f-164b5fd15b1b@1.pkg/1772602159478/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602160435", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7b4183d9-e1c8-4080-a73f-164b5fd15b1b@1.pkg/1772602159478/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602160435"}, "identifier": "7b4183d9-e1c8-4080-a73f-164b5fd15b1b", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A</span><span>本诗的写作背景是安史之乱</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B&ldquo;</span><span>俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。&rdquo;写傍晚秋雨之前的景色，渲染出一种暗淡阴冷的氛围</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D诗歌结尾两句表明诗人急切地希望实现自己的理想，是为解除天下寒士的痛苦</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析正确的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列分析正确的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7b4183d9-e1c8-4080-a73f-164b5fd15b1b@1.pkg/item.json?v=1745244888703", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本诗的写作背景是靖康之乱，作者到了成都，在西郊浣花溪搭了几间茅屋，不想难抵狂风大雨的袭击，屋漏难以入睡，因有此作。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;</span><span>床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。&rdquo;写傍晚秋雨之前的景色，渲染出一种暗淡阴冷的氛围。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;</span><span>八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。&rdquo;写风势迅猛，一个&ldquo;怒&rdquo;字，把秋风拟人化，从而使下一句不仅富有动作性，而且富有浓烈的感情色彩。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>诗歌结尾两句表明诗人急切地希望实现自己的理想，是为解除自己的痛苦，谋求自己的私利。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析正确的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44b